Basic Physics Laboratory I
Description: Selected experiments in the different branches of physics are carried out and written up by the student. One two-hour exercise per week.  Corequisite: PHYS 201 or 231. Premedical and pre-dental students should elect this course along with PHYS 201; it is an option for others.
